          "text": "a survey prepared by a surveyor or a surveyor's certificate showing the planned location of all wind turbines, lot lines, required setbacks and separation distances, existing and proposed structures, access roads, turn-around locations, substations, electrical cabling from the wind energy facility to substations, ancillary equipment, and transmission and distribution lines; and"
